<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MYPD 마이데이터의 첫걸음</title>

    
    <!-- SWIPER -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css"/>
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/default.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/logo-fabicon.png">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about_nav">
        <nav class="navigation">
            <%- include ("./header2") %>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <main>
        <div class="main_pic_bg">
            <div class="city_edit"> 
                <h1>회원정보 수정</h1>
                <p>여러분의 서비스와 테스트데이터를 등록하세요.</p>

                <!-- 비밀번호 재확인 -->
                <div class="mypage_box">
                    <div class="img">
                        <img src="../images/sad.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="edit_pw_check_txt">비밀번호 재확인</h1>
                    <p>회원 정보를 안전하게 보호하기 위해 비밀번호를 다시 확인해요.</p>
                    <form class="mypage_pwcheck" method="post" action="/mypage/editcheck">
                        <label for="pw_check">회원 비밀번호</label>
                        <input type="password" id="pw_check" name="pw_Check" required class="mypage_input">
                        <button type="submit">확인</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                    
            </div>

        </div>

    </main>
</body>
